Package common.math

Class Vector

  • java.lang.Object
    • common.math.Vector
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable
    public class Vector
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Cloneable
    Representation of free vector. All the methods that take a vector as argument require the amount of dimensions of an instance and the argument to be equal. In other case, IllegalArgumentException is thrown (Point.checkDimensions(Point)).
